sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Browser (Templates)
    participant View as Django View
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open Delete confirmation
    UI->>View: GET /note/<id>/delete/
    View->>DB: SELECT Note WHERE id=<id>
    DB-->>View: Note
    View-->>UI: Render note_confirm_delete.html

    User->>UI: Confirm delete
    UI->>View: POST /note/<id>/delete/
    View->>DB: DELETE Note WHERE id=<id>
    DB-->>View: Deleted
    View-->>UI: Redirect to /
    UI-->>User: Note removed from list
